tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:18:34.000Z","msg":"有文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1e10aa1e3f1db672af830f15439afef8ef294d","tid":2344503,"uid":127229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:08:15.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"285135e8b01dda58ec4897a66f591b4aaa91cb8a","tid":2344503,"uid":265217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T19:20:18.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4fd77865824cf0735e435975bd4cacada5e37766","tid":2344503,"uid":313172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"瘋狂出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ddfe0826a27801bcecc8b3b6b56e87647093d86","tid":2344503,"uid":36072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fd77865824cf0735e435975bd4cacada5e37766","tid":2344503,"uid":313172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"瘋狂出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff67257fb7b960b7a8e5e4d5b421a1d52dfeef55","tid":2344503,"uid":60744,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:34:02.000Z","msg":"樓主出文<br />\n<br />\n瘋狂出文=一篇文<br />\n<br />\n有文=冇文<br />\n<br />\n冇文=真係冇文"},{"pid":"00778d70b4d2d6e0bca1efad46f2ccb88761b75e","tid":2344503,"uid":313172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ddfe0826a27801bcecc8b3b6b56e87647093d86","tid":2344503,"uid":36072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fd77865824cf0735e435975bd4cacada5e37766","tid":2344503,"uid":313172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"瘋狂出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda3a826464191acf50823a9ce6e13d219a72ab1","tid":2344503,"uid":323428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T12:20:10.000Z","msg":"瘋狂出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd1a613d56dd0c8714b72fe5ed976e66ee3782b","tid":2344503,"uid":324994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T15:26:43.000Z","msg":"瘋狂出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c368c1658ea72df884cc18c3644bc29d90d2886c","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T15:49:56.000Z","msg":"今晚會有的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455d9e126bfb82fa6f6f86b2be927b674181c83c","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:18:24.000Z","msg":"A. 問她iq題<br />\n<br />\n你凝視拖住她的手，你不但被說是抽水，而且還被叫作deedee，總覺不是味兒。唔好以為妳靚女就可以叫我deedee先得㗎！你甚是不忿，於是決定問她一條IQ題，將她好好羞辱一番：「不如我考妳一條iq題，去沙灘唔𥄫女 估一個明星名？」<br />\n<br />\n「吓，拖住我就係為左問我iq題？」縱使她對你的行為甚是不解，她心裡卻認為你的iq題挺有趣的，於是陷入沉思。<br />\n<br />\n「um...我估係劉心悠，留心游水咪唔會𥄫女！」語畢，你不禁暗叫：拿泥！你被秒殺的一剎，時間侊似停了下來，四周的歡呼聲都聽不入耳。你看著侍應姐姐沾沾自喜的樣子，雖是可愛，卻又帶點囂張。此刻，你既想輕撫她白淨的臉，又想一巴煎落去。但當務之急，還是先編造一個合理的答案，總之，就是不能讓她答對！誰叫你叫我deedee!<br />\n<br />\n「好可惜，係錯嘅。答案其實係陳國邦（李斯）。因為去沙灘唔𥄫女係silly......係咪好輕鬆呢？」說罷，你才鬆開拖住她的手，輕輕放下一句：「唔好再抽我水喇。」<br />\n<br />\n你臨走前，看到了她那不解的眼神，雖然你智商不高，但也明白，你剛才做多了。<br />\n<br />\n新一年的到來，是新的開始，也代表你快要上學了。但是，你還未開始做假期功課，但你記得欖球好像送了自己給你作為聖誕禮物，於是你有個大膽的想法。明天就要交功課了，你決定<br />\n<br />\nA. 叫欖球幫你完成功課<br />\nB. 認真做功課<br />\nC. 弱者先交功課"},{"pid":"302babd262dcd3a336805ebf4309de631922ddbc","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:18:36.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"0f63402fce8eb6c5d1b7038c1f8941e6f2971e2e","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:18:46.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"f6582b2020931b797e5780aeeb6734ffcb4d4844","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:18:56.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"91daf1c2ce103734f510878fafd54d6e599dd0d1","tid":2344503,"uid":258026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:38:35.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"63ee81e7a570e7e1dafae148c005cca808d6047e","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T18:01:51.000Z","msg":"C. 弱者先交功課<br />\n<br />\n已是假期的最後一晚，如果要認真完成所有功課，除非是通宵達旦地做，否則，根本不可能完成。你想過叫欖球幫忙，她卻分心不睱；你亦想過認真做功課，卻有太多題目不會。whatsapp問了好兄弟Kayson如何是好，他竟回你一句：弱者先交功課！<br />\n<br />\n在房間來回踱步，思考片刻，覺得Kayson說得很對，所以決定直接睡覺，功課也不做了。就算沒交功課，也總有同學一起受罰吧！<br />\n<br />\n翌日早上，班房內出現了前所未有的景象。假期後的第一天，大家一回到課室，不是在趕功課，其他人也罷了，竟然連打椿機成員Sarah和全級最壞的凱婷都同流合污。就是借閱別人的功課。你和Kayson見狀，均以不屑的眼神看著大家，暗叫一聲：你們全部都是弱者！<br />\n<br />\n好了，身為強者的你們，終於要向老師解釋了。你和Kayson怔怔的望著miss石，解釋道：<br />\n<br />\nA. 無帶<br />\nB. 強者是不會交功課的<br />\nC. 你教我先識做"},{"pid":"37ce3dcefa6735ebf82ca72b74de9df838f6b409","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T18:02:02.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"ada6e45d2641f2f2f2e25599a3c76896d3150bb0","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T18:02:14.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"6bd070afd961f4f9c2bbbd60071ccc580ccbef3e","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T18:02:27.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"2f6b673466597e2d0863f3ce0f39f8bcb18f1ce5","tid":2344503,"uid":258026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T19:04:46.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"8bf2cfb81ae618ebd4b9bcff42f8eab8b3da41bc","tid":2344503,"uid":251618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"好多文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c798eebfb3ec4faa5934d07f9003ac133360dd87","tid":2344503,"uid":36072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bf2cfb81ae618ebd4b9bcff42f8eab8b3da41bc","tid":2344503,"uid":251618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"好多文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b84fb595724063d656318eb304de5e98317839b","tid":2344503,"uid":118682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20dbbef7788be4900380a516032f249e58ee8063","tid":2344503,"uid":77129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:39:00.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df269590eb20db320981626fc81aa77597ac16c","tid":2344503,"uid":47162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"e7197d9fefe490ac16d7e5856050f78033870092","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T18:49:17.000Z","msg":"B. 強者是不會交功課的<br />\n<br />\n被問到為何沒交功課，你和Kayson都不知如何回答。說忘了帶的話，即是懦夫；說明天再交的話，又是弱者所為。你倆思索片刻，總於有了死亡的覺悟。<br />\n<br />\n「交功課係弱者嘅行為，強者係唔會交！」既然要死，當然要死得轟烈，所以你和Kayson異口同聲地說。然而，你們自詡為強者，卻沒想過老師更強。之後的一個星期，你和Kayson都要一起被罰留堂。由於Miss石要求你們到教員室留堂，所以縱使你們是強者，也不可能逃出她的手掌心。<br />\n<br />\n「唉！咩強者先唔交功課，比你累死。」你倆坐在教員室外的座位，一邊補做功課，一邊聊天。<br />\n<br />\n「信我啦，天降大任於......喂你睇下！」Kayson指着窗外遠處的一對男女，接着道：「上次你問佢IQ題果個女仔喎，佢接腎仔放學嘅！」<br />\n<br />\n聞話，你頓時眼神恍惚，眼前的景象不斷旋轉，彷彿成了萬花筒的碎片似的。你也不曉得是什麼緣故，眺望他倆離開學校時言笑晏晏的樣子，總覺不是味兒。你不知道自己怎麼了，只是渾身不自在，於是決定<br />\n<br />\nA. 原地自轉10個圈<br />\nB. 繼續做功課<br />\nC. 倒立做功課"},{"pid":"37c06648a5a2bf2399690025c0e25b59ec9e4887","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T18:49:27.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"5e8aa491151d05d1dfe95a5cb889ed2bd0cf1f8e","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T18:49:38.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"0ea6f27b7ce0b2ef33d131bc8e7aa3ec0dc8392f","tid":2344503,"uid":303356,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T18:49:49.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"fa59ded559d1da6f7b4858b0d9ff33217414a80d","tid":2344503,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T19:04:19.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"430f3e3253b2da1d6eebb59c9424dfa61fbca1b8","tid":2344503,"uid":77129,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"樓豬啲故已經無咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d7478d0e3cfee3f8f0b7a449b9a984d147fea6","tid":2344503,"uid":60744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"已經唔記得主角問邊個同1q題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a816613663d4d809c87108e9c317440e38ca5d","tid":2344503,"uid":77129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c25610d1db62e8ba429b98d17503430d2ced3f","tid":2344503,"uid":77129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f62ae2e263bba1bfd71ee63eb235a20a5f8e04","tid":2344503,"uid":151927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:12:03.000Z","msg":"樓主人呢"},{"pid":"a48564b3462674011b3be71b7bebc4f7ae3987ad","tid":2344503,"uid":328709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:48:40.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"69520aa4cbd6f365ffd51b3d72e94f38355dabb4","tid":2344503,"uid":155974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T19:54:56.000Z","msg":"故已棄"},{"pid":"e69c1ddb38c325d58ba106e8048ea2b24e88bd57","tid":2344503,"uid":77129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c281250205271522d970db4569272e41a173e0","tid":2344503,"uid":170271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}